.0pt;font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\"'> Noital4u@aol.com\n[mailto:Noital4u@aol.com] <br>\n<b>Sent:</b> Thursday, October 04, 2007 1:25 PM<br>\n<b>To:</b> Lesley Groff<br>\n<b>Subject:</b> Re: jeffrey's puppy<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\",\"serif\";\ncolor:black'>Hi Lesley,</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\",\"serif\";\ncolor:black'>Janet made the phone call this morning to her friend that breeds\nEnglish Springers.&nbsp; The wheels are turning and I have my hopes up that we\nwill find a puppy for Jeffrey.&nbsp; I know how excited he gets, I hate to let\nhim down. Also, my friend Pepper Frazier is having lunch today with the vice\nchairman of Westminster Kennel Club.&nbsp; I asked Pepper to find out if he has\nany ideas for Springer breeders. </span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\",\"serif\";\ncolor:black'>I hope you don't think I am a spoiled brat for trying to have\nJamie with us in NYC.&nbsp; As I said to you, everything happens for a\nreason.&nbsp; I'm sure it will be best for Jamie to be closer to the show\ngrounds and in the mix.&nbsp; I am very grateful for the use of Jeffrey's\napartments.&nbsp; He's a good guy!</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\",\"serif\";\ncolor:black'>I hope to meet you during my visit.&nbsp; It would be fun to have\nyou come see Jamie show.&nbsp; This is an exciting time!</span><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\",\"serif\";\ncolor:black'>Pamela</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:12.0pt'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><br>\n<br>\n<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<div>\n\n<div class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:7.5pt;text-align:center'><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>\n\n<hr size=2 width=\"100%\" align=center>\n\n</span></div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.5pt'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>See what's new at <a\nhref=\"http://www.aol.com?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001170\" target=\"_blank\"\ntitle=\"http://www.aol.com?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001170\">AOL.com</a> and <a\nhref=\"http://www.aol.com/mksplash.adp?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001169\" target=\"_blank\"\ntitle=\"http://www.aol.com/mksplash.adp?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001169\">Make AOL Your\nHomepage</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":0,"avatar_color":"#0f9d58","stars":3,"is_redacted":false},{"id":"024f12018e3aa419a6311ea164dc21f7","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: jeffrey's puppy","date":"2007-10-03T18:13:05.000Z","formatted_date":"Oct 3, 2007","formatted_time":"6:13 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: Noital4u@aol.com [mailto:Noital4u@aol.com] \nSent: Wednesday, October 03, 2007 2:07 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: jeffrey's puppy\n\n \n\nI just called Janet, she knows a Springer judge that also is a breeder.\nShe is going to call him in the morning to find out if he has a male\npuppy for Jeffrey.  If he doesn't he will surely know of another\nbreeder.  We will find one!  This other was just not meant to be.  No\nworries.\n\nPamela\n\n\n\n\n\n________________________________\n\nSee what's new at AOL.com <http://www.aol.com?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001170>\nand Make AOL Your Homepage\n<http://www.aol.com/mksplash.adp?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001169> .\n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTENT=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 12 (filtered medium)\">\n<!--[if !mso]>\n<style>\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n<style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */\n @font-face\n\t{font-family